; pad_and_balance.beancount — pad followed by balance with a mid-period
; transaction. The pad should fill exactly the amount needed so that the
; balance assertion on 2024-03-01 matches.

2024-01-01 open Assets:Bank               USD
2024-01-01 open Income:Salary             USD
2024-01-01 open Equity:Opening-Balances

; On 2024-01-02 pad Assets:Bank from Equity:Opening-Balances.
2024-01-02 pad Assets:Bank Equity:Opening-Balances

; Mid-period transaction adds 200 USD to Assets:Bank.
2024-02-10 * "Paycheck"
  Assets:Bank          200.00 USD
  Income:Salary       -200.00 USD

; Balance assertion: pad must fill 800 so running balance = 1000.
2024-03-01 balance Assets:Bank           1000.00 USD
